                        "meta": {
                            "course-unit-read": "<audio controls>\r\n  <source src=\"https://educate.potential.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/AI-Case-Studies-and-Practical-Usage.mp3\" type=\"audio/mp3\">\r\n  Your browser does not support the audio element.\r\n</audio>\r\n\r\n<h5>Prominent companies have harnessed AI to their advantage.  </h5>\r\n<h5>Google uses AI for more accurate search results, while Tesla's self-driving cars rely heavily on AI for navigation.  </h5>\r\n<h5>But as AI integration deepens, ethical concerns arise, like biases in AI algorithms.  </h5>\r\n<h5>Staying updated on 'AI in the News' can offer insights into its rapidly evolving landscape.  </h5>\r\n<h5>As we embark on this AI journey, balancing its capabilities with ethical considerations becomes paramount. </h5>",
